\newlabel{fig:age_changes}{{9}{12}{\textbf {Age-dependent changes in hallmark interaction strength.} Bars show the change in Spearman correlation between old ($\geq $60) and young ($<$40) groups. Red: strengthened coupling; Blue: weakened coupling. Stars indicate statistical significance.\relax }{figure.caption.12}{}}
